###############Creacion del ambiente en GC ############################

1st. We gonna need a GC Project and permissions to Kubernetes API for that project 


gcloud init 
Ejecutar terrafom
Conectarse al cluster de Kubernetes 
  gcloud container clusters get-credentials k8s-gocd-cluster --zone us-central1-a --project k8s-gocd3
Iniciar helm
  helm init
Instalar despliegue 
  helm install --name my-release incubator/gocd
Exponer puerto
  kubectl expose deployment my-release-gocd-server --type=LoadBalancer --name=my-loadbalancer
Listar puesto expuesto
  kubectl get services

